data.description: Why Rent, When You Can Own! Three levels of living space! Appreciable brick townhouse with low taxes and assessments. Features 3 bedrooms with original hardwood floors in the second level along with full bathroom. The full basement has 2 additional rooms. One is currently being used as an office recently updated and the other as a storage room. Main level has been freshly painted in 2023, good size living room with original hardwood floors. Kitchen includes New Stainless-Steel Refrigerator 2023 and a half bath on this level.  In unit washer 2022 and dryer 2023 plenty of space to create a laundry folding area if desired. Townhouse also features New Furnace 2023, New AC 2023, New Tankless water heater 2023 . Fenced yard for your privacy and one assigned parking space in the back. Plenty of additional parking along frontage road. Conveniently located near restaurants, highway, entertainment and shopping (minutes from Oakbrook mall). Don't wait schedule your showing today! Investor Friendly.
